result:
<st-modal
  title="编辑储物柜"
  size="small"
  v-model="show"
  @ok="onSubmit"
  @cancel="onCancel"
  :confirmLoading="loading.editCabinetStatus"
>
  <st-form labelWidth="70px">
    <st-form-item label="使用状态">
      <a-radio-group v-model="cabinet_business_type">
        <a-radio
          :key="index"
          :value="+item.value"
          v-for="(item, index) in cabinetBusinessTypes"
        >
          {{ item.label }}
        </a-radio>
      </a-radio-group>
    </st-form-item>
  </st-form>
</st-modal>
